WEBVTT

00:01:59.280 --> 00:02:03.130
I wondered: What would a woman

00:02:03.130 --> 00:02:07.800
who had spent over a hundred years 
on the planet think about?

00:02:07.800 --> 00:02:13.020
About her age, about aging, 
about her family,

00:02:13.020 --> 00:02:17.000
about her country or about her democracy?

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:19.360
So I set out, with my brother,
Vijay Jodha,

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:22.360
who is a filmmaker.

00:02:22.360 --> 00:02:27.440
For the next eight years we travelled to 
different parts of India.

00:02:27.440 --> 00:02:33.000
We went to lots of places.
